247
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:45,400
 To nije problem.

248
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,520
 Morate se samo dogovoriti

249
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:47,240
 sa Franjevcima.

250
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,860
 I možete zamisliti

251
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:50,880
 kad sam ujutro u zoru

252
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:51,880
 na sunce otvorio

253
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:53,180
 riječ Božju Efežanima

254
00:13:53,180 --> 00:13:55,440
 probudi se ti što spavaš

255
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,580
