262
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:08,220
 i kapelu pronalazka

263
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:09,040
 Svetog križa.

264
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,440
 To je tako Jeruzalemu

265
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,880
