288
00:14:48,220 --> 00:14:50,080
 Jeruzalem je pun takvih cisterni.

289
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,800
 Bunara.

290
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:55,100
 Kristova greda, križa

291
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:56,580
